  <brief_title>The Effects of Mirtazapine Versus Placebo on Alcohol Consumption in Male Alcohol High Consumers</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Effects of Mirtazapine vs Placebo on Alcohol Consumption in Male Alcohol High Consumers; a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
