  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to study the effects of 8 weeks of treatment with mirtazapine on
      alcohol consumption in alcohol high consuming men. This study is a randomized, double-blind
      placebo controlled clinical trial with parallel group design(N=59).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
